
There are 3 category of design patterns
1. Creational Design patter
2. Structured Design patter
3. Behavioral Design patter

Creational Design patterns - How to smartly handle the creation of objects
** When it comes to object creation it lies down to creational patterns
** How my instances/objects to create
** how to reuse single object or create a new one
** When to create an object

There are some patterns which are-
1. Singleton Design pattern
2. Factory Design pattern